quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,1,"Alif, Lam, Mim.",footnotes:177007:1
  2,2,"This is the Book of Allah, there is no doubt in it; it is a guidance for the pious,",footnotes:177008:1,footnotes:177009:2
  2,3,"for those who believe in the existence of that which is beyond the reach of perception, who establish Prayer and spend out of what We have provided them,",footnotes:177010:1,footnotes:177011:2,footnotes:177012:3
  2,4,"who believe in what has been revealed to you and what was revealed before you, and have firm faith in the Hereafter.",footnotes:177013:1,footnotes:177014:2
  2,5,"Such are on true guidance from their Lord; such are the truly successful."